  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br>Build a formidable station - Expand your little outpost and build up weapons and defenses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/341de0046592f942cba6044ab85e3e34.poster.avif?t=1726318100\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/341de0046592f942cba6044ab85e3e34.webm?t=1726318100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/341de0046592f942cba6044ab85e3e34.mp4?t=1726318100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Defend your station - Encounter countless enemies and threats.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/b5e3e557467f9da598abc04b8d10c2e1.poster.avif?t=1726318100\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/b5e3e557467f9da598abc04b8d10c2e1.webm?t=1726318100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/b5e3e557467f9da598abc04b8d10c2e1.mp4?t=1726318100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unique paths - Collect perks as you defeat enemies and build a powerful arsenal.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/92fe8c972368cd896ea99d88776bf3fa.poster.avif?t=1726318100\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247820/extras/92fe8c972368cd896ea99d88776bf3fa.webm?t=1726318100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"